title: Atahualpa Yupanqui Instrumental (Guitar Solo) LP2CD Flac
description:
On the Harmonia Mundi 5 cd set \"Yupanqui Integrale\" some 11 instrumental guitar solo tracks are missing that you can find on his diverse HM LP\&#039;s and on the Plaene LP 10101  \"Die Andesgitarre\", that is taken from Harmonia Mundi recordings.
This collection takes this LP as starting point and ads four more tracks to the ten on that LP.

1 Malando
2 Vidala Dpolorosa
3 El Bien Perdido
4 El Indio y la Quena
5 Pastoral India
6 La Paloma Enamorada
7 Regreso del Pastor
8 Cachapaya
9 Cancion del Carretero
10 La Amorosa
-------------------------------
11 Don Emiliano, taken from \"Camino del Indio\" Ldx 74631
12 Juan Careno. taken from \"Cancion Para Pablo Neruda\" Ldx 747540
13 Lloran las Ramos del Viento
14 Triste no. 5,  both taken from \"Soy libre! Soy bueno!\" Ldx 74371

Analog to digital transfer using Difitec WavePurity. Flac level 8.
LP scans an some guitar sheet music of three compositions are included
